name: TestComplete Project Suite Settings File
summary: Learn about .TCCFGEXTENDER files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: TestComplete uses projects and project suites to allow you to test different applications. Since you can test a variety of applications at the same time, TestComplete uses files, such as TCCFGEXTENDER, to hold test settings to maintain consistency.

description: Settings file created by TestComplete, a platform used for testing desktop, mobile, and web applications; contains settings for specific testing of a project suite.
